==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mainland
<hw>Main"land`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The continent; the
principal land; -- opposed to <contr>island</contr>, or
<contr>peninsula</contr>.</def> <rj><au>Dryden.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>After the two wayfarers had crossed from the peninsula to the
<qex>mainland</qex>.</q> <rj><qau>Hawthorne.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>mainland China</ent>⟦br⟧
